p-8 lg:gap-0 items-center" data-v-cc0bdda5><div class="lg:order-2 order-2 pb-10 lg:pb-0" data-v-cc0bdda5><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6" data-v-cc0bdda5><h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-paxel-purple" data-v-cc0bdda5>PaxelMarket merupakan marketplace makanan dari Paxel yang memberikan ruang bagi UMKM untuk berjualan dan memperluas jangkauan pasar mereka secara online.</h2></div><span data-v-cc0bdda5></span></div><div class="lg:order-1 order-1 flex justify-center items-start" data-v-cc0bdda5><div class="relative w-full h-[400px] md:h-[355px] lg:h-[500px] overflow-hidden" data-v-cc0bdda5><img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/paxelbucket/revamp/image-jpg-paxelmarket-microsite-basic-service-K8NWAQ1-IX1QPFY-3SUSMXU-3FP2CWL.png" alt="PaxelMarket merupakan marketplace makanan dari Paxel yang memberikan ruang bagi UMKM untuk berjualan dan memperluas jangkauan pasar mereka secara online." class="absolute -top-12 md:-top-20 lg:top-5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 scale-[0.7] sm:scale-[0.7] md:scale-[0.7] lg:scale-[0.9] w-auto object-contain object-top" data-v-cc0bdda5></div></div></div></div></div><!--]--></section><section class="py-16 bg-white" data-v-48bc0329 data-v-9d69c23e><div class="container mx-auto px-4" data-v-9d69c23e><h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-left px-5 md:px-20 mb-12 text-paxel-purple" data-v-9d69c23e>Fitur Unggulan</h2><div class="hidden md:grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-v-9d69c23e><!--[--><div class="rounded-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-v-9d69c23e><div class="flex justify-center mb-4" data-v-9d69c23e><img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/paxelbucket/revamp/icon-paxelmarket-microsite-main-features-X8ITBMU-NXKPKVP-6BT1N0X-CP7SQVR.jpg" alt="Registrasi Toko Kurang dari 1 Menit" class="w-24 h-24 object-contain" data-v-9d69c23e></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3" data-v-9d69c23e>Registrasi Toko Kurang dari 1 Menit</h3><p class="text-gray-700 text-sm" data-v-9d69c23e>Proses registrasi cukup dengan syarat dan ketentuan yang mudah.</p></div><div class="rounded-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-v-9d69c23e><div class="flex justify-center mb-4" data-v-9d69c23e><img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/paxelbucket/revamp/icon-paxelmarket-microsite-main-features-3R257TH-1KQBTTK-YOU63LQ-X3YBVHO.jpg" alt="Pelacakan Realtime" class="w-24 h-24 object-contain" data-v-9d69c23e></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3" data-v-9d69c23e>Pelacakan Realtime</h3><p class="text-gray-700 text-sm" data-v-9d69c23e>Pantau kiriman dengan pelacakan secara langsung dengan SLA pengiriman Sameday &amp; Nextday service</p></div><div class="rounded-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-v-9d69c23e><div class="flex justify-center mb-4" data-v-9d69c23e><img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/paxelbucket/revamp/icon-paxelmarket-microsite-main-features-2VALK6X-WWPRDER-41K6MD0-I7YTHI0.jpg" alt="Berbagai Macam Kategori" class="w-24 h-24 object-contain" data-v-9d69c23e></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3" data-v-9d69c23e>Berbagai Macam Kategori</h3><p class="text-gray-700 text-sm" data-v-9d69c23e>Menerima dan bisa diandalkan dalam mengirimkan berbagai jenis produk frozen, non-frozen atau dry food</p></div><div class="rounded-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-v-9d69c23e><div class="flex justify-center mb-4" data-v-9d69c23e><img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/paxelbucket/revamp/icon-paxelmarket-microsite-main-features-B6R541M-QU27HR3-A1IX0UM-AQJ5EBP.jpg" alt="Harga Terjangkau" class="w-24 h-24 object-contain" data-v-9d69c23e></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3" data-v-9d69c23e>Harga Terjangkau</h3><p class="text-gray-700 text-sm" data-v-9d69c23e>Fleksibilitas ukuran paket sampai dengan dimensi maksimal 50x50x50 cm</p></div><div class="rounded-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-v-9d69c23e><div class="flex justify-center mb-4" data-v-9d69c23e><img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/paxelbucket/revamp/icon-paxelmarket-microsite-main-features-1NMIUOE-BI0EQF8-2X1412X-HQKC8BD.jpg" alt="Commission Fee Flat" class="w-24 h-24 object-contain" data-v-9d69c23e></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3" data-v-9d69c23e>Commission Fee Flat</h3><p class="text-gray-700 text-sm" data-v-9d69c23e>Proses registrasi cukup dengan syarat dan ketentuan yang mudah. Dengan admin fee sebesar 10%</p></div><div class="rounded-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-v-9d69c23e><div class="flex justify-center mb-4" data-v-9d69c23e><img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/paxelbucket/revamp/icon-paxelmarket-microsite-main-features-06RCQ18-A0T7YHU-78I8633-QNPYKN2.jpg" alt="Gratis Banner Ads" class="w-24 h-24 object-contain" data-v-9d69c23e></div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3" data-v-9d69c23e>Gratis Banner Ads</h3><p class="text-gray-700 text-sm" data-v-9d69c23e>Dapatkan banner ads yang bisa anda kelola sendiri sesuai dengan kebutuhan toko anda</p></div><!--]--></div><div class="md:hidden" data-v-9d69c23e><div class="swiper features-swiper" data-v-9d69c23e><!--[--><!--]--><div class="swiper-wrapper"><!--[--><!--]--><!--[--><div class="swiper-slide" data-v-9d69c23e><!--[--><div class="rounded-lg p-6 text-center mb-12" data-v-9d69c23e><div class="flex justify-center mb-4" data-v-9d69c23e><img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/paxelbucket/revamp/icon-paxelmarket-microsite-main-features-X8ITBMU-NXKPKVP-6BT1N0X-CP7SQVR.jpg" alt="Registrasi Toko Kurang dari 1 Menit" class="w-24 h-24 object-contain" data-v-9d69c23e></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3" data-v-9d69c23e>Registrasi Toko Kurang dari 1 Menit</h3><p class="text-gray-700 text-sm" data-v-9d69c23e>Proses registrasi cukup dengan syarat dan ketentuan yang mudah.</p></div><!--]--><!----></div><div class